nodes.text: The twelfth moon of Yout was one of at least twelve moons that orbited the planet Yout, located in the Yout system. The assassin droid KRONOS-327 was sent on a mission to the moon by Ziro the Hutt, a mission which the droid failed. As punishment for his failure, Ziro ordered his other assassin droids to have KRONOS-327 dismantled.
